      </div><p class="focus-in-expand">
        Hi, I'm <strong>Bastian García Pérez</strong><br />
        Backend Software Development using Java Environment + Spring Technologies.
        <br />
        <br />
        I started my software development career after studying Desarrollo de Aplicaciones
        Multiplataforma in Madrid, Spain. Since then I'm a Full Stack Developer with
        2 years of experiece in the field, always focused in backend development,
